  @{B} F2 @{UB}@{FG TEXT} Colour
  @{B} F3 @{UB}@{FG TEXT} Solid
  @{B} F4 @{UB} Previews the brush in box form
  @{B} F5 @{UB} Make/Redo Object
  @{B} F6 @{UB} Select the type of pointer (precise or not)
  @{B} F7 @{UB} Will show the prefs of the current effect.
  @{B} F10 @{UB} Will close the toolbox window

  @{B} Alt x @{UB} Brush Handle
  @{B} Numeric keyboard @{UB}to select brush (0-9)
