 @{FG SHINE}ANIMATION :@{FG TEXT}
  @{B} 1 @{UB}@{FG TEXT} Previous frame
  @{B} 2 @{UB}@{FG TEXT} Next frame
  @{B} 3 @{UB}@{FG TEXT} Go to frame...
  @{B} 4 @{UB} Play animation
  @{B} 5 @{UB} Play animation once
  @{B} 6 @{UB} Ping-pong animation

  During animation playback:
  @{B} Space @{UB} Stop the animation
