@NODE "introduction" "Introduction"

    @{I}Throughout the documentation:@{UI}
@{I}    LMB = Left Mouse Button@{UI}
@{I}    RMB = Right Mouse Button@{UI}
@{I}    Bg = Background@{UI}
@{I}    Fg = Foreground@{UI}

  Paint, Anim and manipulate pictures from 1bit to 24bits

@{B}Requirements:@{UB}

    68030 minimum + Coprocesseur
    OS 3.0 minimum
    Graphics card (Cybergraphx min cgxv41_r71 or Picasso96)
    Jpeg.library
    Render.library
    XPKmaster.library (used to save your 24bit animation)


@{B}Some features of PerfectPaint:@{UB}
     Drawing in 1-24 bits
     Antialiasing
     Spare page
     Stencil
     Symmetry
     Multiple-level undo
     Text with antialiasing, bevel, outline and effects
     Different types of pen
     Animation
     zoom
     Arexx
     Brush: Mapping density, Opacity, Smooth border (24bits)
     Several effects
     .......

Read the documentation for more information.

@ENDNODE
@NODE "installation" "Installation"

Unarchive the file PerfectPaint.lha and copy the
entire "PerfectPaint" drawer wherever you like.

This drawer contains a font called "PfPaint.font" in 'PerfectPaint:FONTS' directory
Copy:
  PfPaint.font
  The PfPaint directory
to your FONTS: directory.

Installation of RexxMast:
If it is not already there, copy the RexxMast
executable to your WBStartup drawer.

Install @{" Render.library " link render.library}
Install @{" Jpeg.library " link jpeg.library}
Install @{" XPKmaster.library " link XPKmaster.library}
Install @{" Asyncio.library " link Asyncio.library}
Install @{" ttengine.library " link ttengine.library}


@{bg shine}@{B} Last version of Cybergraphx V3 can be found here @{bg back}@{UB} 
http://www.vgr.com/v3/cgxv41_r71.lha
ftp://ftp.vgr.com/cgxv41_r71.lha
http://www.vgr.com/meanmachine/cgxv41_r71.lha


@ENDNODE
